      "kind": "group",
      "name": "PkgFrechetDistanceRef",
      "brief": "",
      "detailed": "André Nusser, Marvin Künnemann, and Karl Bringmann This package provides functions for computing an approximation of the Fréchet distance of two polylines in any dimension under the Euclidean metric. Introduced in: CGAL 6.1 BibTeX: cgal:nkb-fd-26a License: GPL This package provides functions for computing an approximation of the Fréchet distance of two polylines in any dimension under the Euclidean metric. Classified Reference Pages Concepts FrechetDistanceTraits Classes CGAL::Frechet_distance::Neighbor_search CGAL::Frechet_distance_traits_2 CGAL::Frechet_distance_traits_3 CGAL::Frechet_distance_traits_d Functions CGAL::bounded_error_Frechet_distance() CGAL::is_Frechet_distance_larger()",
